Company Description: At Building Bridges Christian Counseling, our experienced marriage and family counselors use proven psychological methods coupled with biblical truth to be able to bring joy, life and health to people emotionally, mentally and spiritually. Our team of Christian Counselors frequently help married couples, dating couples and individuals with depression, anxiety, anger, conflict, addictions, phase of life issues and crisis of faith. We have two counseling centers to serve you in the Inland Empire based in Ontario, Ca and Fontana, Ca. Our Ontario location is at 3200 Guasti Rd. Ontario, Ca 91761 and our Fontana location is at 7623 East Ave Fontana, Ca 92336. They are both freeway close, near Rancho Cucamonga,Upland, Chino, Chino Hills, Montclair, Claremont, Pomona, Rialto, Corona and Eastvale. We try to build bridges to the things that are important to our clients through Christian counseling for married couples, dating couples, families and individuals. Bridges to family members, to God, to success and financial stability, to happiness and peace. Bridges require planning, a clear goal, diligence, time and resources. It may not be easy, but few things worth having are easily obtained. We have numerous Christian Counselors that would love to assist you in anything you might need in your life so call today to schedule an appointment! 909-303-0563

Canyon Ridge Hospital is a full-service, 105-plus-bed psychiatric facility. Operational since 1989, it offers treatment for individuals with emotional, behavioral and chemical dependency problems. The hospital serves adolescents and adults in Riverside, Los Angeles and Orange counties in California. Canyon Ridge Hospital offers individual therapy and discharge planning services. The hospital provides an intensive outpatient chemical dependency program that includes family participation and group therapy to focus on relapse prevention skills. It helps in the improvement of social, communication and anger management skills. The hospital operates 24 hours a day, seven days a week. Canyon Ridge Hospital is managed by Psychiatric Solutions.

Company Description: Since 1955, West End Family Counseling Services has been providing community mental health services in the West San Bernardino County. Based in Ontario, Calif., it offers services, such as department of behavioral health outpatient services, community services and united way rancho community clinic. The service providers of the organization include social workers, masters-level counselors, psychologists, psychiatrists, and supervised graduate interns. West End Family Counseling Services offers a range of programs, including elder and dependent adult outreach program, school-based counseling programs, parent education program.
